{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/Algorithm/220212-union-find/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"개발일기","author":"gintooooonic","siteUrl":"https://gintooooonic.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"gintooooonic/gintooooonic.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9b0d36a4-1685-5182-83d1-9f22785b9226","excerpt":"Union Find 알고리즘이란 과  연산을 제공한다고 하여 Union Find 다른 이름은 Disjoint Set Union (DSU) 두 집합을 합치고, 임의의 두 원소가 같은 집합에 있는지 빠르게 알 수 있음 동작 과정 두 개의 연산을 제공  : x가 속한 집합과 y가 속한 집합을 합치는 연산  : x…","html":"<h2 id=\"union-find-알고리즘이란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#union-find-%EC%95%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A6%98%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"union find 알고리즘이란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Union Find 알고리즘이란</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">Union</code>과 <code class=\"language-text\">Find</code> 연산을 제공한다고 하여 Union Find</li>\n<li>다른 이름은 Disjoint Set Union (DSU)</li>\n<li>두 집합을 합치고, 임의의 두 원소가 같은 집합에 있는지 빠르게 알 수 있음</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"동작-과정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%8F%99%EC%9E%91-%EA%B3%BC%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"동작 과정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>동작 과정</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>두 개의 연산을 제공</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">union(x, y)</code> : x가 속한 집합과 y가 속한 집합을 합치는 연산</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">find(x)</code> : x가 속한 집합을 대표하는 원소를 반환</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>각 원소는 본인의 부모 원소를 갖게 되고, 최상위 부모 원소가 집합의 대표 값이 됨</li>\n<li>각 원소마다 본인의 부모 원소를 저장하는 배열이 필요</li>\n<li>마치 트리와 같음</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"구현\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84\" aria-label=\"구현 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>구현</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cpp\"><pre class=\"language-cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 각 원소의 부모를 보관</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> par<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">10000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 재귀적으로 루트 원소를 찾아 반환</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> par<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>par<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// x와 y의 루트 원소를 찾아 하나를 다른 하나의 부모로 지정</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// C++에서는 union이 키워드이므로 다른 이름을 사용하였음</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">merge</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    y <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> par<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// par 배열 초기화</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">10000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">++</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        par<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> i<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// merge &amp; find</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Find와 Union 연산을 최적화하면 평균적으로 <code class=\"language-text\">O(α(n))</code> 시간이 소요</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">α(n)</code>은 <a href=\"https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%EC%95%84%EC%BB%A4%EB%A7%8C_%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98\">Ackermann 함수</a>의 역함수</li>\n<li>상수 시간에 가까울 정도로 n에 대해 매우 느리게 증가</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>일반적인 알고리즘 문제 풀이에서는 최적화 없이 사용해도 괜찮을 것으로 보임</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"find-연산-최적화\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#find-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0-%EC%B5%9C%EC%A0%81%ED%99%94\" aria-label=\"find 연산 최적화 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Find 연산 최적화</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cpp\"><pre class=\"language-cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> par<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> par<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>par<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>기존 코드는 루트 원소와의 거리가 먼 경우 재귀 호출이 많이 일어나기 때문에 최악의 경우 <code class=\"language-text\">O(n)</code> 시간 소요</li>\n<li>루트 원소를 찾아 올라가는 경로의 모든 원소들을 루트 원소에 직접 붙여줌으로써 경로를 단축</li>\n<li>첫 번째 Find에서는 시간 차이가 없겠지만, 그 이후에는 상수 시간에 찾을 수 있을 것</li>\n<li>평균적으로 <code class=\"language-text\">O(log(n))</code> 시간 소요</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"union-연산-최적화\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#union-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0-%EC%B5%9C%EC%A0%81%ED%99%94\" aria-label=\"union 연산 최적화 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Union 연산 최적화</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"cpp\"><pre class=\"language-cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> set_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">10000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 먼저 1로 초기화</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">merge</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    y <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>set_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> set_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            <span class=\"token function\">swap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        par<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        set_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> set_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>y<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>기존 코드는 항상 두 번째 집합이 첫 번째 집합에 붙도록 방향이 고정</li>\n<li>최악의 경우 트리의 depth가 <code class=\"language-text\">O(n)</code>이 될 수 있음</li>\n<li>크기가 작은 집합이 크기가 큰 집합에 붙도록 최적화</li>\n<li>depth가 작은 트리를 큰 트리의 루트에 붙이는 꼴이 됨</li>\n<li>평균적으로 <code class=\"language-text\">O(log(n))</code> 시간 소요</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://cp-algorithms.com/data_structures/disjoint_set_union.html\">Disjoint Set Union - Algorithms for Competitive Programming</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Algorithm/220212-union-find/#union-find-%EC%95%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A6%98%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\">Union Find 알고리즘이란</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Algorithm/220212-union-find/#%EB%8F%99%EC%9E%91-%EA%B3%BC%EC%A0%95\">동작 과정</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/Algorithm/220212-union-find/#%EA%B5%AC%ED%98%84\">구현</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/Algorithm/220212-union-find/#find-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0-%EC%B5%9C%EC%A0%81%ED%99%94\">Find 연산 최적화</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Algorithm/220212-union-find/#union-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0-%EC%B5%9C%EC%A0%81%ED%99%94\">Union 연산 최적화</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Algorithm/220212-union-find/#reference\">Reference</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Union Find 알고리즘","date":"February 12, 2022"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Algorithm/220212-union-find/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Spring/220210-singleton/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"싱글톤 패턴"}},"next":null}},"staticQueryHashes":["2486386679","3128451518"]}